{
  "lessonId": "4ecdd9e3-53c7-4c94-b4d0-c78facf9af8d",
  "lessonOrderIndex": 0,
  "lessonTitle": "Understanding Effective Leadership",
  "lessonDescription": "Explore what makes leaders effective, how leadership influences organizational success, and which qualities and behaviors distinguish great leaders from poor ones.",
  "titleSlideSettings": null,
  "slides": [
    {
      "orderIndex": 0,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "The Importance of Leadership",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Leadership plays a crucial role in the success of any organization.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>Effective leaders inspire and motivate their team members to achieve common goals.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Poor leadership can lead to confusion, low morale, and decreased productivity.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "callout",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "mode": "callout",
            "variant": "info",
            "title": null,
            "html": "<p>The quality of leadership within an organization directly shapes its culture, performance, and long-term impact in the community it serves.</p>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 1,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Qualities of Effective Leaders",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Effective leaders share a common set of core qualities that enable them to guide their teams successfully:</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>Effective leaders possess qualities such as good communication skills, empathy, and integrity.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>They are able to listen to their team members and provide guidance and support.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>They lead by example and are accountable for their actions.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 2,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Leading by Example",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Leading by example means demonstrating the behaviors and values you expect from your team.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "image_gallery",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "images": [
              {
                "url": "https://ylmnbbrpaeiogdeqezlo.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/canva-exports/gansid-modules/module-9/images/lesson_00/slide_03_image_01.png",
                "alt": "Leading by example illustration",
                "caption": null
              },
              {
                "url": "https://ylmnbbrpaeiogdeqezlo.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/canva-exports/gansid-modules/module-9/images/lesson_00/slide_03_image_02.jpg",
                "alt": "Leading by example illustration",
                "caption": null
              },
              {
                "url": "https://ylmnbbrpaeiogdeqezlo.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/canva-exports/gansid-modules/module-9/images/lesson_00/slide_03_image_03.jpg",
                "alt": "Leading by example illustration",
                "caption": null
              },
              {
                "url": "https://ylmnbbrpaeiogdeqezlo.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/canva-exports/gansid-modules/module-9/images/lesson_00/slide_03_image_04.jpg",
                "alt": "Leading by example illustration",
                "caption": null
              }
            ],
            "mode": "gallery",
            "aspectRatio": "16/9",
            "objectFit": "cover",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>When leaders set a positive example, it encourages their team members to do the same.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>This creates a culture of accountability and fosters trust within the organization.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "blockType": "callout",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "mode": "callout",
            "variant": "info",
            "title": null,
            "html": "<p>Actions speak louder than words. When you model the behavior you expect, your team is far more likely to follow suit.</p>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 3, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 3,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Communication Skills",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Effective leaders are skilled communicators who can clearly convey their expectations and vision.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>They actively listen to their team members and encourage open and honest communication.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Good communication helps to build strong relationships and resolve conflicts.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h3>Key Communication Practices for Leaders</h3>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>Practice active listening — give your full attention and acknowledge what you hear.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Be clear and concise when conveying expectations and goals.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Encourage two-way communication — make it safe for team members to share ideas and concerns.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Provide regular, constructive feedback.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 3, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 4,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Adaptability and Flexibility",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Effective leaders are adaptable and flexible in their approach.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>They can navigate through challenges and embrace change.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Being open to new ideas and perspectives allows leaders to make informed decisions.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Adaptable leaders recognize that the path to success may need to be adjusted as circumstances evolve.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "decimal",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "callout",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "mode": "callout",
            "variant": "info",
            "title": null,
            "html": "<p>In today's fast-changing environment, the ability to pivot and adapt is one of the most valuable leadership traits an organization can benefit from.</p>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 5,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Empowering Others",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Effective leaders empower their team members by delegating tasks and giving them autonomy.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>They trust their team's abilities and provide opportunities for growth and development.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Empowering others fosters a sense of ownership and increases motivation.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h3>How to Empower Your Team</h3>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>Delegate meaningful work, not just routine tasks.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Give team members the authority to make decisions within their areas of responsibility.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Provide the resources and support they need to succeed.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>Celebrate their achievements and learn from setbacks together.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 3, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 6,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Emotional Intelligence",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "image_gallery",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "images": [
              {
                "url": "https://ylmnbbrpaeiogdeqezlo.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/canva-exports/gansid-modules/module-9/images/lesson_00/slide_07_image_05.jpg",
                "alt": "Emotional intelligence illustration",
                "caption": null
              }
            ],
            "mode": "single",
            "objectFit": "contain",
            "displaySize": "lg",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Emotional intelligence is the ability to understand and manage one's own emotions and those of others.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>Effective leaders with high emotional intelligence can empathize with their team members and build strong relationships.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>They are aware of the impact their emotions have on others and can regulate their responses.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "disc",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<h3>The Four Components of Emotional Intelligence</h3>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 3, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "blockType": "table",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "columns": [
              { "id": "col-component", "label": "Component", "align": "left" },
              { "id": "col-description", "label": "Description", "align": "left" }
            ],
            "rows": [
              { "id": "row-self-awareness", "cells": { "col-component": "Self-Awareness", "col-description": "Recognizing your own emotions and their impact." } },
              { "id": "row-self-regulation", "cells": { "col-component": "Self-Regulation", "col-description": "Managing your emotions and impulses constructively." } },
              { "id": "row-empathy", "cells": { "col-component": "Empathy", "col-description": "Understanding and sharing the feelings of others." } },
              { "id": "row-social-skills", "cells": { "col-component": "Social Skills", "col-description": "Building and managing healthy relationships." } }
            ],
            "first_column_header": true,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 4, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "orderIndex": 7,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Continuous Learning and Improvement",
      "status": "published",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Effective leaders are committed to continuous learning and self-improvement.</p>",
            "mode": "standard",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "content_list",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "items": [
              { "html": "<p>They seek out new knowledge, attend workshops, and read books to enhance their skills.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>By continuously learning, leaders can stay updated with industry trends and adapt their strategies accordingly.</p>", "animation": "none" },
              { "html": "<p>A growth mindset — the belief that abilities can be developed — is a hallmark of effective leaders.</p>", "animation": "none" }
            ],
            "bullet_style": "decimal",
            "enable_animations": false,
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 1, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "callout",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "mode": "callout",
            "variant": "info",
            "title": null,
            "html": "<p>The best leaders are always students. Committing to your own growth sets a powerful example for your entire organization.</p>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 2, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 3
          }
        }
      ]
    },
